content.p: The School of Economics has a culturally diverse teaching and research environment. We combine excellence and innovation in teaching with an international reputation for rigorous and topical research of the highest quality. We offer broad programmes of study, combining all of the core analytical and quantitative techniques required by modern economics graduates. Economics students share their reasons for choosing us. Sir Clive Granger Building University of Nottingham University Park Nottingham, NG7 2RD
